2.caption: 1989 Major League Baseball All-Star Game
2.description: The NL got off to a fast start off Dave Stewart in the first on RBI singles by Kevin Mitchell and Howard Johnson. The AL would counter in spectacular fashion in their half when game MVP Bo Jackson golfed the second pitch by Rick Reuschel, a low sinker, out in deep center. Wade Boggs followed with a homer to tie it.
2.inspected:Radio announcers: Brent Musburger, Jerry Coleman and Johnny Bench
2.inspected:TV announcers: Vin Scully, Tom Seaver and Ronald Reagan (first inning only)
